Class SCUtil

java.lang.Object
  com.paypal.android.sdk.payments.base.SCUtil
All Implemented Interfaces:
Parcelable
public class SCUtil
extends Object
implements Parcelable

Utility class to allow the UI to send tracking notifications to the SiteCatalyst tracking system. The class maintains a token which prefixes all uploads. this token is reset every 30 minutes. Not clear if this is needed or not but nobody wants to remove it. The class surfaces one API, track(TrackingPoint point) with an extension to supply a list of ErrorBase objects for tracking errors too. The point is one of the set of tracking points defined for this app. Given the tracking point the whole string to be sent is assembled and sent.
